We are looking for a Senior Leader to lead Growth Marketing for Tencent Game’s portfolio of games and brands in the overseas markets. This role will contribute to the acceleration of our business growth with a focus on user acquisition, user activation and solution expansion. The ideal candidate has a strong track record in growth marketing, marketing automation, innovation marketing technology, analytics, paid media and content optimization across all channels. Candidates should possess expertise and passion for creating a big impact and build innovative new systems and processes from the group up.;
Key Responsibilities;
• Oversee all marketing analytics and optimization strategies.;
• Lead our acquisition efforts and strategic roadmap for social, display, search and affiliate marketing.;
• Partner with publishing teams to drive growth and ensure campaigns are in alignment with brand positioning and strategic
goals.;
• Continuously work to improve ROI through A/B testing, channel analysis, daily monitoring/reporting, etc.;
• Create and manage attribution model and efficiency of digital marketing spend.;
• Proactively stay abreast of industry trends and search for new opportunities to grow channels and refine strategies and tactics.;

We are looking for a marketing expert who will contribute the overseas growth marketing team with a focus on user acquisition, user activation and solution expansion. Candidates should possess expertise and passion for developing and executing challenging acquisition campaigns with a focus on Display, Social, Search, and Affiliate Marketing.;
